e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"diu,返大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce7b111c4b1026ef50d44eee8caf74354d2524a","tid":2062012,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d9e1218cfdd6f9d60b54cd77b3b9549a02374b3","tid":2062012,"uid":28114,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T23:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/rc-06122020101415.html/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fmeiti%2Frc-06122020101415.html%2F3.jpg&h=025b2ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遠程會議服務平台Zoom創辦人、中國移民袁征（Eric Yuan）（Zoom 公司官網）<br />\n<br />\nZoom危機越處理越大兩邊不討好<br />\n<br />\n身在中國國內的金融學者賀江兵說，自己不會使用這類線上通訊或會議軟件，是因為隱私顧慮，&ldquo;在那裡參會就像是裸奔&rdquo;。他不認為Zoom創辦人袁征的華裔背景應受關切，因為外國企業想進入中國市場遇到的困境與批評，一直以來都沒改變。<br />\n<br />\n他說，&ldquo;牆頭草嘛！他（Zoom）想雙方都討好，結果可能都得罪了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n兩黨議員寫公開信八問袁征要求說明<br />\n<br />\n美國政界對Zoom的批評與質疑，也在國會山莊引燃，形成兩黨共識。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨籍聯邦參議員盧比奧（Marco Rubio）與民主黨籍聯邦參議員懷登（Ron Wyden）12日領銜，一共十二名兩黨參議員公開致信給袁征，他們對Zoom聽從中國政府指示的做法&ldquo;深表關切&rdquo;，也提出八大疑問，要求袁征解釋。包括要求Zoom明確指出，是按照哪一部中國法律、關閉美國用戶王丹與周鋒鎖的帳號？Zoom決定關閉李卓人帳號，內部決策過程為何？哪一個中國政府有關部門提出要求？Zoom是否定期和中國政府分享數據？如果有，又是哪些數據信息？<br />\n<br />\nZoom今年五月聘請前白宮國安顧問麥克馬斯特（HR McMaster）擔任獨立董事，他當時指出，希望&ldquo;協助實現Zoom要成為世界上最安全視頻通信平台的承諾&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nZoom預告，將在今年六月底公佈改進自身全球發展政策的透明度報告，虛擬世界的網路主權爭奪戰，Zoom會是觀察風向標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/rc-06122020101415.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fmeiti%2Frc-06122020101415.html&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=02f571cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/rc-06122020101415.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;中國政府從未要求提供外國用戶的數據信息，中國政府部門只關心本地會議&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死 胖虎唔打你係佢打緊大雄 唔係因為佢冇能力打理"},{"pid":"bef02aa637cb155e8d2ee2f49678c5d4fbbd68c1","tid":2062012,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"917cef2e6a8a238ffeec6643291456ec1e99650f","tid":2062012,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"中共間諜公司"},{"pid":"0772890d6cb033e41f00f525f136676c197f75b6","tid":2062012,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11024f557654175d6ac9ad3443b3b5f45ef4c26","tid":2062012,"uid":32371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d7299dfdce7d09c15a039d034bb49e43473f067","tid":2062012,"uid":60451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"係美國遵守中國法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4213e4ddef30d8f4fccb622a7436be4392d3039","tid":2062012,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"他建議，美國大學應該聯合行動，像是發表共同聲明，要求Zoom明確承諾並寫明原則規範，不能讓美國的學術自由受侵害。<br />\nOn9 左膠，仲信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941df9488aedcc17b169e0928155d5ea2430d043","tid":2062012,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"你有say 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1594973fb12dc96655badb251df78ba6ec270a34","tid":2062012,"uid":123895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"識玩緊係用部乾淨機keep住用黎開六四/人權meeting睇佢敢唔敢del"},{"pid":"6883c81d6847fb7d26f8e2dc3e71d11c856f67ee","t